Build process:

  Create an NSIS instller script for Windows.


Ports:

  Windows
    Cross-develompent tools:
      MinGW cross-compiler:  http://www.mingw.org/
      http://members.lycos.co.uk/alexv6/Cross_mingw_building_HOWTO.html

    Toolkits:
      GTK+ for Windows:      http://www.gimp.org/~tml/gimp/win32/
      GTK+ for Windows runtime installer:  http://members.lycos.co.uk/alexv6/

      Other libraries needed for Windows:  http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/
	(freetype, jpeg, libpng, tiff)

    Installers:
      NSIS:        http://nsis.sourceforge.net/
      MAKEMSI:     http://www.labyrinth.net.au/~dbareis/makemsi.htm
      WiX:         http://sourceforge.net/projects/wix/

  MacOS X
    http://www.macgimp.org/index.php?topic=gtk
